\chapter{The Stay A While queue API}

Stay A While is the EECS queueing system.
We want to access its documented REST API both from Python and from the
shell.

We therefore provide two interfaces:
first, a class, [[StayawhileSession]], that wraps the HTTP API;
second, a Typer CLI rooted at [[kthutils stayawhile]].

We extract the Python module from the following root chunk.
