\section{Common request handling}

All API calls share the same authentication header and JSON decoding logic.
We therefore centralise them in a single request helper.
<<[[StayawhileSession]] constructor>>=
self.api_key = api_key or get_api_key()
self.base_url = (base_url or get_base_url()).rstrip("/")
self.__session = session or requests.Session()
